am.\", \"from\": 389, \"to\": 467, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 432, \"end\": 439, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9031116626540554, \"rank\": 0.10722906287469758, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After finishing in fifth place in the women's +78-kilogram event at the Summer Olympic Games in Tokyo in 2021, she was in tears but announced in front of camera: \\\"I will come back.\", \"from\": 468, \"to\": 648, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 564, \"end\": 569, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"score\": 0.8930174154835587, \"rank\": 0.11953077101011528, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo_bid_for_the_2020_Summer_Olympics\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Back then, in many people's eyes, Xu was the Chinese national team's rising star who started as a sparring partner.\", \"from\": 648, \"to\": 764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 694, \"end\": 715, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9818168675542261, \"rank\": 0.010487318454013505, \"text\": \"Chinese national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her failure at the Olympics was a real blow to her confidence and caused her to doubt herself.\", \"from\": 765, \"to\": 859, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The national team went to train overseas in 2022,\\\" Xu told China Media Group (CMG).\", \"from\": 859, \"to\": 943, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 919, \"end\": 936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"China Media Group\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_Media_Group\"}, {\"begin\": 938, \"end\": 941, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"score\": 0.9735318986499176, \"rank\": 0.024911504264327713, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We spent a long time in other countries, but did not achieve many good results.\", \"from\": 944, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Maybe I ran into the bottleneck at that time.\", \"from\": 1025, \"to\": 1070, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I doubted myself.\", \"from\": 1071, \"to\": 1088, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The Chinese national team has been through some changes in recent years, including switching from Chinese coaches to French ones and to Georgian ones today.\", \"from\": 1088, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1093, \"end\": 1114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9818168675542261, \"rank\": 0.010487318454013505, \"text\": \"Chinese national team\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1187, \"end\": 1194, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9031116626540554, \"rank\": 0.10722906287469758, \"text\": \"Chinese\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1206, \"end\": 1212, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9393590793819555, \"rank\": 0.05671666170916309, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 1225, \"end\": 1233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgian_language\", \"score\": 0.9293074288975994, \"rank\": 0.05887338621094025, \"text\": \"Georgian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Georgian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Xu benefitted a lot from these changes.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1285, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Her biggest advantage was stamina, which enabled her to always move quickly in the fight.\", \"from\": 1286, \"to\": 1375, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"One of her major shortcomings was the lack of enough methods to score.\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1446, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Xu Shiyan (R) of China competes with Hilal Ozturk of T\\u00c3\\u00bcrkiye in the women's +78-kilogram bronze medal bout at the Judo World Championship in Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates, May 23, 2024.\", \"from\": 1448, \"to\": 1636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1451, \"end\": 1457, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shiyan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Shiyan\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shiyan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shiyan\"}, {\"begin\": 1465, \"end\": 1470, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"score\": 0.9696020026766834, \"rank\": 0.03134081032676708, \"text\": \"China\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/China\"}, {\"begin\": 1590, \"end\": 1621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Abu_Dhabi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Abu Dhabi, United Arab Emirates\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.