er target,\\\" Xu told CMG.\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2448, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2398, \"end\": 2403, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999945691798, \"rank\": 5.430731231270533e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2444, \"end\": 2447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"score\": 0.9735318986499176, \"rank\": 0.024911504264327713, \"text\": \"CMG\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Order_of_St_Michael_and_St_George\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I want nothing but the gold.\", \"from\": 2449, \"to\": 2478, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"If I am given the chance, my goal is always the top on the podium.\\\"\", \"from\": 2479, \"to\": 2546, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\", \"from\": 2548, \"to\": 2808, \"entities\": []}]}"